name: 金·穆尔哈瑟
introduction: Kim Mulhauser was born in Teaneck, New Jersey, but spent most of her childhood in Windham, NH. She is of German, Ukrainian, Czechoslovakian, Irish, and French Canadian descent. Kim developed a passion for the arts early on. Kim set out to study Forensic Science, but along the way she uncovered a passion for acting. Kim has competed in various pageants including Miss New Hampshire USA 2014 and is also a print model. She has landed various roles in theatre, commercials, music videos, short films, and feature films.
